[resource]
script = ExtResource("2_i6qdo")
Icon = ExtResource("1_mq6yh")
Label = "Chunk Management"
Tooltip = "Chunk Management Tool

Used to create, delete and change chunk settings.

[INFO]
Chunk cell merge modes:
• CUBIC: The most blocky of all the modes. Has minimal smoothing between cells.
• POLYHEDRON: Blocky terrain with slight cell smoothing (DEFAULT CHUNK STATE).
• ROUNDED_POLYHEDRON: A good 50/50 mix between having smooth and blocky terrain.
• SEMI_ROUND: Mostly smooth terrain with the occasional blocky cells.
• SPHERICAL: All the terrain will become smooth. This mode looks the most unnatural for the algorithm.

[SHORTCUTS]
• CTRL+LMB: Change the currently selected chunk to the hovered chunk."
AttributeSettings = SubResource("Resource_mq6yh")
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://brkjbcthwswel"
